<item>
            <title>[HIVE-27804] Implement batching in getPartition calls which returns partition list along with auth info</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-27804</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hive.getPartitions() methods returns partition list along with auth info in one HMS call. These calls when made on wide tables(&amp;gt; 2000 columns) with very large number of partitions(100,000+) can cause memory related issues when the data is being transferred from HMS to HS2 using Thrift calls. These APIs can be optimised by using PartitionIterable implementation where the partition list if fetched in batched of a smaller size rather than one huge call.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
